  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK761">
<l>uṟuppamain tūṟañcā velpaṭai vēntaṉ</l>
<l>veṟukkaiyu ḷellān talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The army which is complete in (its) parts and conquers without fear of wounds is the chief wealth of the king.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
